source_code.code:
class Foo extends bug.Bug{
    static class Helper{
        static int method(){return number;}
    }
    static class Stub{}
}

public class Bug {
    protected static int number;
}

Bug.WithStack:
Eclipse refuses to move the method into class Stub, even though manually 
moving the method's text gives a legal result.

----------------------- Foo.java ------------------
class Foo extends bug.Bug{
    static class Helper{
        static int method(){return number;}
    }
    static class Stub{}
}

----------------------- bug/Bug.java ---------------
package bug;
public class Bug {
    protected static int number;
}
This works for me using N20051018-0010 or greater

Closing as works for me

