Bug.WithStack:
J2EE team has deleted AddUtilityJARMapCommand so the addJavaProjectAsUtilityJar method in AddModuleDependenciesCommand needs to be updated. It is currently commented out with a TODO. Here is a conversation I had with John Lanuti on this:
